MODKEY -> LEFT ALT KEY

-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | Slash   | Spawn Dmenu                   |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------|
| MODKEY                | Return  | Spawn Terminal                |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------|
| MODKEY                | T       | Toggle Bar                    |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | J       | Focus next window             |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | K       | Focus previous window         |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | I       | Increase window # in master   |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | U       | Decrease window # in master   |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | H       | Decrease master space         |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | L       | Increase master space         |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | Z       | Put active window to master   |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | Tab     | Switch between last 2 tags    |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | Q       | Kill active window            |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY | Shift        | T       | Set tiled layout              |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY | Shift        | F       | Set floating layout           |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY | Shift        | M       | Set monocle layout            |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | Space   | Switch between last 2 layouts |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY | Shift        | Space   | Toggle active window floating |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | 0       | View all tags                 |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY | Shift        | 0       | Tag current window all tags   |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | N       | Next tag                      |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY | Shift        | N       | Prev tag                      |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY                | Tag Key | Focust tag                    |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY | Ctrl         | Tag Key | Also focus tag                |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY | Shift        | Tag Key | Move active window to tag     |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| MODKEY | Ctrl | Shift | Tag Key | Also put active window to tag |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
